#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""Resident controller prototype for the iMessage Autopilot skill.

The controller supports synthetic JSONL and an explicit-path, read-only
Messages-shaped SQLite source. The SQLite source is replica-tested only. There
is no Contacts, Apple Events, permission, network, or real dispatch adapter.
"""

